
file header:

8	uint8_t[8]	--> File signature = "chachaXX"
4	uint32_t	--> Major prog version
4	uint32_t	--> Number of rounds
8	uint64_t	--> Number used once
8	uint64_t	--> Encrypted data size
---
32 bytes

